-- EditorClientV2 (Data Editor client) -- MOVED SERVER-SIDE 2026-07-11.
--
-- The full editor (~120 KB) used to ship here in StarterGui, replicating its entire source to
-- EVERY player even though only authorized editors (see ServerStorage.Dev.EditorAdmins) can use
-- it. It now lives in ServerStorage/Dev/AdminGui/EditorClientV2 and is cloned into an authorized
-- editor's PlayerGui by Bootstrap (applyAdminAttribute -> syncAdminEditorGui) only while their
-- server-stamped IsAdmin attribute is true, so non-admins never receive the code.
--
-- This stub stays mapped in default.project.json so Rojo OVERWRITES the old full-editor
-- LocalScript in each published place with this no-op (no manual Studio delete needed). It builds
-- no UI, binds no key, and makes no remote calls. Do NOT add logic here -- edit the ServerStorage
-- template (ServerStorage/Dev/AdminGui/EditorClientV2.client.luau) instead.
